		<IntegralSystemProject>$(SolutionDir)Projects\IntegralSystem\IntegralSystem.vcxproj</IntegralSystemProject>
		<CaratProject>$(SolutionDir)Projects\Carat\Carat.vcxproj</CaratProject>
